5 SECTION 2. EXTRA HELP. There is hereby authorized, for the State Board
6 of Election Commissioners for the 2025-2026 fiscal year, the following
7 maximum number of part-time or temporary employees, to be known as "Extra
8 Help", payable from funds appropriated herein for such purposes: twenty (20)
9 temporary or part-time employees, when needed, at rates of pay not to exceed
10 those provided in the Uniform Classification and Compensation Act, or its
11 successor, or this act for the appropriate classification.
12
13 SECTION 3. APPROPRIATION - OPERATIONS. There is hereby appropriated,
