14 Any carry forward of unexpended balance of funding as authorized herein, may
15 be carried forward under the following conditions:
16 (1) Prior to June 30, 2025 2026 the Agency shall by written statement set
17 forth its reason(s) for the need to carry forward said funding to the
18 Department of Finance and Administration Office of Budget;
19 (2) The Department of Finance and Administration Office of Budget shall
20 report to the Arkansas Legislative Council all amounts carried forward by the
21 September Arkansas Legislative Council or Joint Budget Committee meeting
22 which report shall include the name of the Agency, Board, Commission or
23 Institution and the amount of the funding carried forward, the program name
24 or line item, the funding source of that appropriation and a copy of the
25 written request set forth in (1) above;
26 (3) Each Agency, Board, Commission or Institution shall provide a written
27 report to the Arkansas Legislative Council or Joint Budget Committee
28 containing all information set forth in item (2) above, along with a written
29 statement as to the current status of the project, contract, purpose etc. for
30 which the carry forward was originally requested no later than thirty (30)
31 days prior to the time the Agency, Board, Commission or Institution presents
32 its budget request to the Arkansas Legislative Council/Joint Budget
33 Committee; and
34 (4) Thereupon, the Department of Finance and Administration shall include
35 all information obtained in item (3) above in the biennial budget manuals
36 and/or a statement of non-compliance by the Agency, Board, Commission or
